column1: NGR is Waverley Court at the 1900 stated altitude.
1910s record has a different observer and stated altitude is 400 ft and gauge may be 100m N. Big gap between observations.
Gauge moved 0.75 miles SW to Park Road on 1 Jan 1901.
The 1900s record susggests the move may have been in 1902 but the observer is in Park Road in the 1901 census
